# Content Creation and Management

## Topic Creation

### Topic Builder Tool
**[topic-builder.html](mdc:topic-builder.html)** + **[topic-builder.js](mdc:topic-builder.js)** provides a visual interface for creating quiz topics.

### Topic Structure
Topics are stored as JSON files in **[topics/](mdc:topics)** directory. Examples:
- **[ceska_turistika.json](mdc:topics/ceska_turistika.json)** - Czech tourism questions
- **[vanoce.json](mdc:topics/vanoce.json)** - Christmas-themed questions
- **[harry_potter_gryffindor.json](mdc:topics/harry_potter_gryffindor.json)** - Harry Potter topics

### Question Format
Each topic contains questions with:
- Question text
- Multiple choice answers
- Correct answer index
- Optional media (images/audio)

## Quiz Assembly

### Quiz Builder Tool
**[quiz-builder.html](mdc:quiz-builder.html)** + **[quiz-builder.js](mdc:quiz-builder.js)** combines multiple topics into complete quizzes.

### Quiz Storage
Complete quizzes are saved in **[quizzes/](mdc:quizzes)** directory as JSON files.

## Media Support

### Supported Media Types
- **Images**: Stored in **[images/](mdc:images)** directory
- **Audio**: Stored in **[audio/](mdc:audio)** directory

### Media Integration
Media files are referenced in question JSON and displayed during quiz gameplay. See **[MEDIA_FEATURES.md](mdc:MEDIA_FEATURES.md)** for detailed media functionality.

### Test Media Files
- **[test-media.json](mdc:test-media.json)** - Example with media references
- **[test-media-local.json](mdc:test-media-local.json)** - Local media example

## AI Content Generation

**[prompt-generator.html](mdc:prompt-generator.html)** + **[prompt-generator.js](mdc:prompt-generator.js)** helps create AI prompts for generating quiz questions automatically.

